condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 2, Section II | Description :Borrower shall monitor and evaluate, and cause Gansu to monitor andevaluate progress of the project and prepare Project Reports for each semester, with reports due March 15 and September 15 eachyear, starting March 15, 2013. | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :PA, Annex A to Schedule, para 5(e) | Description :QWSSC shall, not later than December 31, 2013, submit afinancial performance improvement plan. | Due Date :31-Dec-2013

Finance Agreement :PA, Annex A to Schedule, para 5(f) | Description :Starting January 1, 2015, the sum of QWSSC's operatingrevenues and non-operating revenues will be no less than equal to the sum ofits operating costs, including depreciation and taxes;debt service requirements; and funds required for other operating investments. | Due Date :01-Jan-2015

Finance Agreement :PA, Schedule, Section I A para 2 | Description :Gansu shall, not more than 3 months after the Effective Date orprior to commencing bidding for works, employ or cause to be Gansu to employ qualified consultants acceptable to the Bank to assistQingyang Municipality, Xifeng District and project participants in project management and supervision. | Due Date :24-Dec-2012
Finance Agreement :PA, Schedule, Section I B | Description :Gansu shall ensure that the Project is carried out in accordance withthe provisions of the Anti-Corruption Guidelines. | Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :PA, Schedule, Section I C | Description :Gansu shall implement the EMP and RAP in accordance with theirrespective terms and report on progress with compliance. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA, Schedule, Section I F | Description :Gansu shall cause Xifeng to (a) not later than 12 months aftereffectiveness, prepare and furnish to the Bank, an action plan for the improvement of parking, an action plan for the improvementof public transport services, and an action plan for the improvement of safety of 3 road corridors, and (b) promptly carry out suchplans as agreed with the Bank. | Due Date :24-Sep-2013

Finance Agreement :PA, Schedule, Section II A | Description :Gansu shall monitor and evaluate the project progress and preparesemi-annual reports, due March 15 and September 15, starting September 15, 2012 | Frequency :Yearly
